    "date": "2023-03-24T14:10:53Z",
    "text": "Aerial Intelligence-collection Revelation Act of 2023 or the AIR Act\n\nThis bill requires the Department of Defense to provide written notification to Congress if any foreign surveillance object (e.g., a balloon) enters the national airspace system without prior approval. Such notification must be submitted to Congress not later than 24 hours after the object enters the national airspace system."
